  "texts": [
    "Strategic planning, digital competencies, and the creation of new digital businesses are particularly relevant to the discussion of digital transformation.",
    "Organizational strategy, IT capabilities, culture, management, government policies, digital technologies, market competition, and digital platforms are some of the internal and external factors considered when determining digital transformation.",
    "The digital transformation has repercussions for economies, societies, and cultures.",
    "We are aware of the challenges posed by the ever-evolving nature of the economy, the job market, and the marketplace.",
    "In conclusion, this study has conducted a thorough analysis of global research on the digital transformation of small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs)."
  ]
}